casebody.data:
Josh FINKELMAN, on behalf of himself and the Putative class, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
NATIONAL FOOTBALL LEAGUE, NFL Ventures, L.P., NFL Properties, L.L.C., NFL Ventures, Inc., NFL Enterprises, L.L.C., Defendants. M-795 September Term 2018
M-796 September Term 2018
080501 Supreme Court of New Jersey. APRIL 4, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-795) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's Opinion (M-796) is denied.
